00:27.610 --> 00:29.487
Should we get some white, too?

00:31.239 --> 00:32.782
Kind of, help age it?

00:32.866 --> 00:34.784
-Get some what?
-[Robert] White.

00:35.410 --> 00:38.455
[Robert] I was thinking of getting this
to hang something in the tree.

00:40.915 --> 00:42.250
It would be cool.

00:43.168 --> 00:44.252
What?

00:44.878 --> 00:48.673
